data.description:
Nestled on a quiet, tree-lined street, this small home exudes an undeniable charm that captures the heart at first glance. The large fenced backyard provides a manageable canvas for gardening enthusiasts without overwhelming those who prefer low maintenance.
In essence, this ideal home seamlessly blends functionality with aesthetics, and easy to maintain.
The house has been cooled with 1 window a/c unit and 2 portable units that will be included with the purchase. NO HOA!
Sellers will leave 3 security cameras, already installed.
NEW ROOF will be installed!
The location is very convenient and District 11 is highly sought after. 
Restaurants, theater, COS airport, and shops on Powers are very close and convenient.
MORE PICS COMING SOON

Seller is willing to offer concessions specifically for a buyer’s rate buydown program that will lower rate by 2% for the first year. This offer does require seller’s preferred lender to be used. Specific terms and rates are subject to borrower approval.
